org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.tools.offlineImageViewer

Class ImageVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.tools.offlineImageViewer.ImageVisitor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TextWriterImageVisitor

    abstract class ImageVisitor
extends Object
    An implementation of ImageVisitor can traverse the structure of an Hadoop fsimage and respond to each of the structures within the file.
